net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite.editor

Class IPv4Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite.editor.IPv4Address

  • class IPv4Address
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a transient immutable data class to represent an IPv4 Address. The intention is that any instance of this class is a valid IPv4 address, as a product of four bytes. However for persistence/convenience, one can invoke toString() to get a String representation.
